### <a id="redis_queue_size"></a>Redis Queue Size
<table>
    <tr>
        <th width="25%">Description</th>
        <td><p><strong>Use</strong>: An unusual spike in the number of queued metrics can indicate that PCF Healthwatch Workers are unable to
